[16.70433, "o", "\u001b[33mcommit 650dba427e0a9dcd118f41a4c5e35c8017550a5a\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\nAuthor: Test User <test@example.com>\u001b[m\r\nDate:   Sat Sep 13 17:54:33 2025 +0000\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n    Move to Stanford\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mdiff --git a/_includes/about.md b/_includes/about.md\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mindex 5322c14..7561d9e 100644\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1m--- a/_includes/about.md\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1m+++ b/_includes/about.md\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[36m@@ -1,3 +1,3 @@\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[31m-I am a sixth year PhD student at the [Paul G. Allen School of Computer Science & Engineering](https://www.cs.washington.edu/) at The University of Washington, \u001b[m \b\u001b[31mwhere I am advised by [Tim Althoff](http://www.timalthoff.com/). I am affiliated with [UW NLP](https://twitter.com/uwnlp).\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[32m+\u001b[m\u001b[32mI am a Postdoctoral Researcher at Stanford CS.\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n \u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[31m-**I am looking for a full time job!** If you think we would be a good match, please reach out. Previously, I was a Student Researcher at [Google Research](http\u001b[m \b\u001b[31ms://research.google/), an ML Research Intern at [Apple Health AI](https://machinele"]
